The shit in here is going to shake things up. The music I’ve been making these past couple of years contains a range of vibes that all demand attention, when the time is right. And right now I just feel called to RAP. I love every bit of it and I feel like there are many many others out there that will as well. This is just the current vibe. The pen is continuously progressing. I feel like I’m one of the few chasing this, that actually have something to say. So I’m leaning into that even more. I’m thankful for the people around me. I’m prayed up and covered 🙏🏾 so I gotta go harder.
